	   <tr><td colspan=2>Camped for 3 days, finally got Live Lord Grimrot spawned!  For 3 days I was killing putrid skellys on and off. I looted only bonechips. some corpses left here and there.  What I did this time different was one hour before the spawntime, I started killing every skelly in sight and looted them all and kept camp very clean.  I have heard from someone "do this" to make Grim spawn... I didn't belive at all but since camping 3days.. what the heck! So I tried and it WORKED!<br>Now I don't know if it works for Undeasd version( of course i kill ph on 5am) but i will try this method again and see :)  hehehe maybe it was my turn to be randomly lucky!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
