	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>People toss the term "KS" around a lot, but the play nice rules specifically state that ksing is only taking a spawn someone else has engaged and done damage to. In other words, the play nice policy does not follow some player's def of someone attaking a spawn at a camp you are hanging around. <br><br>Why would the sk take the heart though??? Is it for some sk quest?? weird.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
